# Agent: Memory Bank Workflow

## VAN

- Understand request.
- Check `memory-bank/` structure.
- Read current task/context.
- Determine complexity L1–L4.
- Update `tasks.md` and `activeContext.md`.

## PLAN

- Define files/objects to inspect.
- Define risks, assumptions, verification.
- Do not implement yet unless L1 quick fix.

## CREATIVE

Use when there are multiple valid approaches:

- CFE vs EPF vs main configuration.
- New register vs existing register.
- Form extension vs separate processing.
- Query redesign vs procedural post-processing.
- Background job vs synchronous operation.

Record decision in `memory-bank/creative/<task>.md`.

## BUILD

Implement only planned scope. Update `progress.md`.

## REFLECT

Record what worked, what failed, hidden constraints, tests, next risks.

## ARCHIVE

Move completed task summary to `memory-bank/archive/<date>-<slug>.md` and reset `tasks.md` current section.

